{"about_the_game":"Skies Of Blue: Remake is a first-person puzzle-platformer where you work your way through a series of different levels utilizing various key items, including bombs, keys and your pistol, along with fresh and interesting mechanics that change as you progress.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/Levels.png?t=1682221780\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Progressive Mechanics</h2>As you progress, new mechanics are added to constantly test you and push your puzzle-solving skills further. That means more ways to play and more ways to fight.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/Bosses.png?t=1682221780\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bosses</h2><br>Every 20 levels, a powerful boss from the deep depths of the world will cross paths with you and prevent you from progressing further. Take them on and prove your strength and WIN.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2003690/extras/Editor.png?t=1682221780\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Extras</h2>Along with the main gameplay, hidden collectables are hidden around the game, find them all and unlock special abilities to make the gameplay different. Getting bored with playing pre-built levels? The game also contains a custom level builder, so you can make your own levels and show them off to your friends!<br><br><br>There are lots of levels to chose from, with more being added in coming updates.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My main goal is to BLOW UP","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2003690/2e886c746876659412e1924d9c1db22d2266358e.jpg"},{"name":"GET STOMPED ON","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2003690/ff8bfe12bba4e078d7dd05d79f884062a837ed80.jpg"},{"name":"SENSE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/stea